name: Sal Weirdo
description:
#075 Sal Weirdo - Greek Church - 1/1 HEN Animated Portrait. 
Sal works in the back of the bowling alley and maintains the famous 69 lanes. He is missing 4 fingers, averages 270 a game, hates wearing underwear, doesn’t believe in socks and invented the 7-10 banana split sundae that he likes to serve to guests during birthday parties, while wearing a gorilla suit. After a long shift you can find him in the karaoke lounge belting out Karma Chameleon by Culture Club, a tribute to every red, gold, and green bowling ball he’s ever had to retire.

Limited collection of #100 unique AI born #WEIRDOS
